comment: Whether Johnny Depp is hired back as Jack Sparrow or Grindelwald has nothing to do with Amber Heard, and her casting in Aquaman 2. She has effectively forever labelled herself as an untrustworthy liar, a narcissist, and a manipulator. It's because of people like her that the cause of true victims suffers. I would neither encourage nor support any enterprise that would work with her, or hire her. My personal ethical and moral choice is not beholden to some studio who can't contract away their director and actress, who will perpetually stain their legacy. There's _no way_ I'm going to the theatre to watch Aquaman 2, if Amber Heard is in it.
